admin/node_modules/
admin/dist/
cmd/payserver/admin_dist/*
!cmd/payserver/admin_dist/index.html
!cmd/payserver/admin_dist/.gitkeep
# Local-build binary produced by `make build` or `go build ./cmd/payserver`.
# Anchored to the repo root so the pattern doesn't also swallow the
# cmd/payserver/ source directory (a bare `payserver` matches any path
# component named "payserver" and silently blocks `git add cmd/payserver/...`).
/payserver
